metadata.name: Same AF
metadata.description:
Same AF, 2021, JPG, 871 x 751 Pixels 72 Resolution (293 KB)

The digital collage has three primary elements. It consists of the background, an open book in the foreground, and two text messages located above and below the book. The background image is Length 1748 by Anna Maria Garthwaite. It's cropped with a gradient of lilac violet to mint green applied from top to bottom. A 2GB memory card is overlayed on the left page and manipulated to create a holographic effect. The text message on the top appears in an Apple iPhone messages blue bubble with the HAHA Tapback. The message reads "I know I'm all ready confused". The bottom text messages include one with a heart Tapback. The text for the first message reads "Same AF". The second message reads, "it's like the black box idea in coding, or ur work lolol, u don't really have to understand what's inside the box to use the box. I just read shit and am like okay fine shoving $100 into that box now lmao".
